snippet.title: Launch Trailer | HAWKED
snippet.description:
The ultimate treasure hunt starts now. HAWKED is a free online Extraction Shooter full of adventure, exploration, and ancient treasures to plunder. Play for free today on PS5, PS4, Xbox Series X|S, and Windows PC: https://playhawked.com 

Play on PS5 and PS4: https://playhawked.com/l/playstation
Play on Xbox Series X|S: https://playhawked.com/l/xbox
Play on MY.GAMES Launcher: https://my.games/launcher 
Play on Steam: https://playhawked.com/l/steam

Connect with HAWKED:

Discord: https://discord.gg/hawked 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/HAWKEDGame/
X/Twitter: https://twitter.com/PlayHAWKED
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/playhawked/
